'''Timaziɣin tigmuḍanin''' nɣ '''Timaziɣin n ugmuḍ''' gant yat trabbut n tutlayin timziɣin ittusawaln g [[Libya]] d [[Miṣra|Miṣṛa]]. Tkcm gi-s [[Tutlayt tawilant|Tawilant]], [[Tutlayt tasknit|Tasknit]], [[Tutlayt Tasiwit|tasiwit]] d [[Tutlayt taɣdmisit|taɣdimsit]]<ref>Aikhenvald, Alexandra Y. & A. Ju. Militarev. 1984. Klassifikacija livijsko-guančskih jazykov. In ''IV vsesojuznaja konferencija afrikanistov "Afrika v 80-e gody: itogi i perspektivy razvitija" (Moskva, 3-5 oktjabrja 1984 g.)'', vol. II, 83-85. (Tezisy Dokladov i Naučnyh Soobščenij IV). Moskva: Institut Afrika Akademii Nauk SSSR, as cited in Takács, Gábor. 1999. ''Development of Afro-Asiatic (Semito-Hamitic) Comparative-Historical Linguistics in Russia and the Former Soviet Union''. (LINCOM Studies in Afroasiatic Linguistics 02). München: LINCOM Europa, p. 130</ref>.

Ɣ umata, ar ttussiḍannt tutlayin timaziɣin tigmuḍanin zɣ tdurabbut n [[tutlayin tijanatin]] n tmaziɣt tagafayt.

== Assinw ==
[[:en:Maarten Kossmann|-{Kossmann}-]] (1999:29, 33)<ref>Maarten Kossmann, Essai sur la phonologie du proto-berbère, Rüdiger Köppe:Köln.</ref> ar tnt ibṭṭu f snat trubba:
* Yat gi-s [[Tutlayt taɣdimsit|Taɣdimsit]] d [[Tutlayt Tawilant|Twilant]]. Snat ad zɣ tutlayin timaziɣin titrarin ka ad yarin -{*β}- n [[Tutlayt tamaziɣt taqburt|Tmaziɣt taqburt]] (-{Proto-Berber}-) am "-{β}-"; ɣ mani yaḍn ar ttaḍu ''-{h}-'' nɣ tt akkʷ laḥ<ref name=":0">Kossmann 1999:61.</ref>.
* Tayyaḍ gi-s [[Tutlayt Tanfust|Tanfusit]] (amr [[Tutlayt Tazwarit tatunsit|Zuwara d unẓul n tuns]]), [[Tutlayt tasknit|Tasknit]] (-{El-Foqaha}-) d [[Tutlayt Tasiwit|tsiwit]]. Drant tutlayin-ad mnnaw isllwitn d [[Tutlayin tijanatin|Tajanat]] ula d tiyyaḍ (s umdya, asnfl n -{*ă}- s -{ə}-<ref>[[:en:Karl-G. Prasse|Karl-G. Prasse]]. "The Reconstruction of Proto-Berber Short Vowels", in ed. James & Theodora Bynon, ''Hamito-Semitica'', The Hague/Paris 1975.</ref> d ticki n -{*β}-<ref name=":0" />)
[[:en:Roger Blench|-{Blench}-]] (-{ms}-, 2006) ismma tid am tutlayin timzirgin, d tantlayin gr taskiwin; Zun d ''-{Ethnologue}-,'' ar ittsmmu [[Tutlayt Tanfust|Tanfust]] am [[Tajanat tagmuḍant]]<ref>[http://rogerblench.info/Language/Afroasiatic/General/AALIST.pdf AA list], Blench, ms, 2006</ref>.

